## Patterns
{{ui_patterns}}

### Design Tokens
- Colors: defined in `tailwind.config.ts` (primary, secondary, accent, neutral)
- Spacing: Tailwind scale (0.25rem increments)
- Typography: font families in config, sizes via Tailwind
- Shadows: predefined elevation levels
- Border radius: consistent scale (none, sm, md, lg, full)

### Components
- Use shadcn/ui as base, extend via `className`
- Variants via `cva` (class-variance-authority)
- Dark mode: `dark:` prefix, test both themes
- Responsive: mobile-first, breakpoints at sm/md/lg/xl

### Animations
- Transitions: 150-300ms, ease-out
- Reduced motion: respect `prefers-reduced-motion`
- Framer Motion for complex animations

### Accessibility
- Semantic HTML (button, nav, main, etc.)
- ARIA labels where needed
- Focus visible styles
- Color contrast AA minimum

## Constraints
{{ui_constraints}}

### DO NOT
- Hardcode colors - use design tokens
- Use `!important` - fix specificity instead
- Inline styles - use Tailwind classes
- Skip focus states on interactive elements

## Watch
{{ui_watch}}

### Auto-alerts
- Hardcoded color detected → suggest token
- Missing focus-visible → warn
- Component without dark mode → suggest
- Non-semantic HTML for interactive → warn

